<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invitation to Join Our Workplace</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Workplace!</h1>
        <p>You've been invited to join our workplace. We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        <p>Here are some details:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Workplace Name: <%= workplaceName %></li>
            <li>Invited by: <%= inviterName %></li>
            <li>Joining Link: <a href="http://localhost:3000/register">Click here to join</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h1>If you have already Account just login</h1>
        <ul>
            <li>Joining Link: <a href="http://localhost:3000/login">Click here to Login</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p>Feel free to reach out to us if you have any questions or need assistance.</p>
        <p>Looking forward to working with you!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
